{
  "stem": "7273.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I met my first boyfriends there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the Jugenbund.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And lots of, as you say, boys and girls, met and married.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was through-- yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Through meetings of people and going out together and having excursions together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that made us closer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, that was one day during the week, if I remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the evening, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was so-- today you would say 'backwards kept,' because I remember I was 16 years of age, and when we finished, I wasn't allowed to go  in my own home.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My nanny came and picked me up, so that wouldn't exist today.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father was too strict, I think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe today's time gives me the idea, but he was a real strict father. 7 o'clock, I had to be home.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And heavens forbid it was later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very happy memories.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had things and did things not everybody could do because it was fairly expensive to travel or to go to the theater or to play tennis.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And here it doesn't seem to be expensive, but at the time I did these things, it was quite expensive.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, actually, nothing was-- by my parents-- nothing was too expensive for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There wasn't a thing I wouldn't have to make me happy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was-- I was quite privileged child, because not only that I had a nanny, but I remember I had a lady coming to my place.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she taught me languages.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had, in the high school, Latin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was a bit hard for girls.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I had the help at home for that as well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had somebody for English.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
